O. D. CLARK, Sheriff of Toole County, Montana, Appellant, v. John H. HAMILTON, Receiver of Sunburst Oil & Refining Co., et al., Appellees. No. 7224. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. July 24, 1933 Hall & McCabe, of Great Palls, Mont., for appellant. Molumby, Busha & Greenan, of Great Palls, Mont., for appellees.

Before SAWTELLE, Circuit Judge, and NORCROSS, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal herein dismissed; mandate forthwith.
